6:
Don't worry, sir! I'll see that this gets
to your granddaughter for sure!
8:
And I won't forget to tell her you're fit
as a fiddle!
12: Oh! Hi, Alk! Hi, Light! Hi, Stella!
16:
Got another package there?
Business is picking up now that it's
the holidays, huh?
19:
You bet! This time, I'm headed for
the village on the other side of the
woods!
23:
You and Baloosh remind me of
Santa.
27:
...It is rumored that a monster now
frequents those woods. Will you be
all right?
32:
Wait, really? Oh no... What'll we do,
Baloosh? The only road to the village
goes through that forest!
36:
I know!

Um, guys... Do you think you could
come with me?
38:
I know I sound like a total amateur. I
mean, it's my job to make deliveries,
but...
40:
That grandpa really cares about his
granddaughter... I'd feel so bad if
something were to happen to his
present!
43: I-I'll pay you for your time!
52:
We have no need of payment. It is
reward enough to accompany you
on this quest.
55:
Yeah. You don't ever have to feel
nervous about asking us for a favor,
okay?
59:
Thanks, guys!

We're really lucky to have them as
friends, huh, Baloosh?
71:
Wonder where that monster we
heard about was...
74:
What does it matter now? Our task
was to see that no harm befell
Aureo.
78:
Anyone home? I've got a special
delivery for a special girl!
81:
A present from grandpa!

Yay! I wonder what it could be!
83: Did you say thank you, young lady?!
85:
Don't worry about it! I've also got a
message for you from your father,
ma'am. He says that at the rate he's
recovering, he'll be up and dancing
by New Year's!
88:
Oh, Dad... He kept going on and on
about how he was going to find the
perfect present this year, but then
he dislocated his kneecap.
89:
It had him feeling pretty down, so
thank goodness for delivery folk like
you. You've made our whole family
very happy.
97:
WAAAAAAH! MOMMY! IT TOOK
GRANDPA'S PRESENT!
101:
It? Was THAT the monster we heard
about?
104:
Probably. It recently moved into the
forest. It doesn't hurt anyone, thank
the stars, but it IS a terrible little thief.
107:
Well, we'd better go teach it to
respect other people's stuff!
113:
Urk!

I-I cannot retrieve your present if
you do not unhand me.
116:
*sniffle* But what if you get hurt,
bunny doll?
119:
She seems to be fond of fluffy
objects.
128:
You're right, Baloosh! This is no time
to be standing around! You stay
here and take care of the kid, Light!
135: Found you! Give back that present!
139:
That's a gift from a grandpa to his
favorite granddaughter. If you steal
it, you'd be ruining their holidays...
146: Gu gu! Guin, gu gu gu, gu guin?!
152:
Thanks for understanding, little
guy.

And thanks for talking some sense
into him, Baloosh!
179:
Oh! Almost forgot to say something
super important...
186:
Hehehe... Thank you! Happy holidays
to you too!
191:
Thanks for your help, everyone. I
couldn't have done it without you!
194:
Though I was forced to be a doll, I
am still glad I came today.
197:
Aureo, never have I seen a living
soul more dedicated to spreading
joy than you are.
